title: Recent Life Updates: Dating, Anxiety, Austin City Limits, & More!
itunes:title: Recent Life Updates: Dating, Anxiety, Austin City Limits, & More!
description:
In this week’s episode, Kimberly Cobb recaps what's been going on in her life lately! The steps she's been taking to take control of her anxiety, recent dating life updates, her recent adventures (day trip to Galveston, Pumpkin Nights, & Austin City Limits Festival), and more!

 

Follow for weekly episodes of the "My Lips Aren't Sealed" podcast, where I discuss dating, fashion, entertainment, travel, pop culture, and more from my life. Thanks for listening!
